{"tid":1819232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1月11日 幹你娘貼爆","createTime":"2020-01-10T15:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T15:58:19.000Z","uid":200120,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e13fe37ff4a74f187aab2f093a02481802ccd475","tid":1819232,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"我之前是在公司印文宣的，而我貼文宣的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘貼爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘貼爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次貼的文宣就是雞巴一大疊。撕一貼十，撕十貼百。整條街也貼爆，跟把整個公司的A4紙全貼光沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月A4紙用了二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"914ae1af2addadf41e77cde83102faa7fecaf313","tid":1819232,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"聽日一齊幹你娘貼爆"},{"pid":"09ac3ea09c1c07eccaaca1dafa9f9ee0b993b80e","tid":1819232,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"幹你娘推爆。"},{"pid":"eb7fef12e1aedbcd2f082657f8b520f0b3197250","tid":1819232,"uid":321854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"一天虧損一箱 你根本是A4紙塞肛門吧"},{"pid":"c51a8dba4b46ffd6dddcd8173704c1fb370bfd21","tid":1819232,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞巴國瑜</span>"}]}